8️⃣ Throttling vs Debouncing (frontend question)
Concept	Meaning
Throttling	Allow once every X time
Debouncing	Run only after activity stops

Example:

Scroll → throttle

Search input → debounce

9️⃣ Interview-ready definition 🎯

“Throttling is a technique used to control the rate of requests or actions over time to protect system resources and prevent abuse.”

🔟 Bonus: what happens when throttled?

Usually:

HTTP 429 status

Retry-After header

Delayed execution

